show.description: For just one night, the fiery Anusha — daughter of a housemaid — forces the innocent Rashmi to impersonate her in a scheme to deceive billionaire Aditya. But that night spirals into a dangerous illusion — of deceit, desire, and mistaken identities. Because in that world, falling in love... could be fatal!
